title: DORK Diaries
author: Rachel Renée Russell
genre: Fiction, Realistic Fiction, Humor, Children’s / Middle‑Grade
description: A bestselling series of diary‑style novels following 14‑ to 15‑year‑old  as she navigates the ups and downs of middle school: friendship, crushes, bullies, school drama, and humorous everyday adventures — told through her diary entries, doodles, and comic‑style drawings.
